===Noun===
'''kittiwake''' (''plural'' '''kittiwake''' or '''kittiwakes''')

# Either of two small [[gull]]s (''Rissa tridactyla'' or ''R. brevirostris'') of the North [[Atlantic]] that nest in colonies on sea cliffs and spend the winter on the open ocean.

